App*
  back -> Exit?

  Exit?
  Go To Previous State?
  Go To Next State?

  Loading Screen*
    Loading App State*
      app state loaded -> Okay To Authenticate?
      app state failure -> App Error

    Okay To Authenticate?
      session token available? -> Validating Session Token
      no session token available? -> Hold Loading Screen

    Hold Loading Screen
      next -> Landing Screen

    Validating Session Token
      token valid -> App Inside
      token invalid -> Hold Loading Screen

  Landing Screen
    sign up -> Intro Screen
    sign in -> Sign In

