      back -> Page 1
      next -> Page 3

    Page 3
      back -> Page 3
      next -> Page 4

    Page 4
      back -> Page 3
      next -> Sign In

  Sign In
    Enter Phone Number Screen*
      No Phone Number Error*
        try sending -> Okay To Send Phone Number?
        recover account -> Recover Account

      Bad Phone Number Error
        dismiss -> No Code Error

      Phone Number Server Error
        dismiss -> No Code Error

      Okay To Send Phone Number?
        blank? -> No Phone Number Error
        not blank? -> Sending Phone Number

      Sending Phone Number
        server accepted -> Enter Code Screen
        server rejected -> Bad Phone Number Error
        server failure -> Phone Number Server Error

    Enter Code Screen
      back -> Enter Phone Number Screen

      No Code Error*
        try sending -> Okay To Send Code?
        resend code -> Resending Code

      Bad Code Error
        dismiss -> No Code Error

      Code Server Error
        dismiss -> No Code Error

      Resending Code
        server success -> Code Resent
        server failure -> Code Server Error

      Code Resent
        try sending -> Okay To Send Code?
        resend code -> Resending Code

      Okay To Send Code?
        blank? -> No Code Error
        not blank? -> Sending Code

      Sending Code
        server accepted with new account -> Sign Up
        server accepted with existing account -> App Inside
        server rejected -> Bad Code Error
        server failure -> Code Server Error

